  <entry>
    <title>ocaml_ch_01</title>
    <url>/2020/11/10/ocaml-ch-01/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="OCaml-Code-Snippets"><a href="#OCaml-Code-Snippets" class="headerlink" title="OCaml Code Snippets"></a>OCaml Code Snippets</h1><h3 id="局部定义"><a href="#局部定义" class="headerlink" title="局部定义"></a>局部定义</h3><figure class="highlight ocaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> x = <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="keyword">let</span> y = x + x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="keyword">let</span> z = y + y <span class="keyword">in</span> x + y + z;;</span><br><span class="line">- : <span class="built_in">int</span> = <span class="number">7</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><code>in</code> 语法形式化语义 (let x = 1 in x + x) = (x + x)[x := 1] = 1+1 = 2</p>
<h3 id="普通递归形式斐波那契数列"><a href="#普通递归形式斐波那契数列" class="headerlink" title="普通递归形式斐波那契数列"></a>普通递归形式斐波那契数列</h3><figure class="highlight ocaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="keyword">rec</span> fib x = </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> x &lt; <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">then</span> <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> x = <span class="number">1</span> || x = <span class="number">2</span> <span class="keyword">then</span> <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> fib(x - <span class="number">1</span>) + fib(x-<span class="number">2</span>);;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i = <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">to</span> <span class="number">20</span> <span class="keyword">do</span></span><br><span class="line">    printf <span class="string">"fib[%d] = %d\n"</span> i (fib i)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">done</span>;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="尾递归形式斐波那契数列"><a href="#尾递归形式斐波那契数列" class="headerlink" title="尾递归形式斐波那契数列"></a>尾递归形式斐波那契数列</h3><p>此时相当于转换成了循环形式，<strong>loop 0</strong> -&gt;<strong>loop 1</strong> -&gt; <strong>loop …</strong> -&gt; <strong>loop n</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight ocaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> fib_tail  n = </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="keyword">rec</span> loop i a b =</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> i &gt; n <span class="keyword">then</span> <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> i = n <span class="keyword">then</span> a</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> loop (i+<span class="number">1</span>)(b)(a+b) <span class="keyword">in</span></span><br><span class="line">    loop <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">1</span>;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i = -<span class="number">2</span> <span class="keyword">to</span> <span class="number">20</span> <span class="keyword">do</span></span><br><span class="line">    printf <span class="string">"fib_tail[%d] = %d\n"</span> i (fib_tail i)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">done</span>;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
